Class LookUpSpectrumLibXX

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class LookUpSpectrumLibXX
extends java.lang.Object
    Algorithm base on paper by Nathan Edward and Ross Lippert LNCS 2452, pp. 68-81, 2002 Use to generate peptide candidates that match precursor mass and at least K b/y ions to the top N most intense peaks in the database
    Author:
    bugouzhi
